			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/CTY_Main_A\r\n- Use ReCon command \"goto 52 3 -138\"\r\n- \"killcombat\" to kill all the Sahuagin after they appear and attack.\r\n- This dialogue will play after a short delay, between a player who was in that combat and one of the civilians here."
				},
